        <p>Delve into the rich industrial history by visiting the Museum Of Bath at Work. Explore this history by visiting the Bowlers Factory and Workshop or even take the opportunity to learn more about Baths working life with an array of displays, allowing you to have a glimse into the citys evoloution across the years.</p>
